   <S PAR='25' RSNT='1' SNO='25'>To study life for the sake of knowledge is very complicated, but for experience it s very simple.</S>
   <S PAR='26' RSNT='1' SNO='26'>Even a little baby can live.</S>
   <S PAR='27' RSNT='1' SNO='27'>After being conceived a little baby can live even before it is born.</S>
   <S PAR='28' RSNT='1' SNO='28'>To live is easy.</S>
   <S PAR='29' RSNT='1' SNO='29'>We have never taught any child to breathe, yet right away after birth they breathe.</S>
   <S PAR='30' RSNT='1' SNO='30'>To live is simple.</S>
