   <S PAR='32' RSNT='1' SNO='32'>Because we all have been trapped, entangled, wrapped up, and bound with so many Christian things.</S>
   <S PAR='33' RSNT='1' SNO='33'>In this Perfecting Training I have been speaking for at least three months on living Christ.</S>
